.946} 1.01 \\mathbf{1.01} TABLE V: Consolidated operating points for the injection-op, \nstep-window, steering-site, and method ablations (small-music, fp32; n = 36 n{=}36 clips per point, 12 12 prompts × 3 \\times\\,3 seeds). Δ \\Delta w2t is the wav2taste target shift vs. the matched α \n= 0 \\alpha{=}0 baseline; Δ \\Delta CLAP is the independent semantic check ( bold once it has flipped negative, i.e. off the genuine window); FAD is degradation vs. baseline. The four groups are read \nin the steering results (Section IV-C ). Axis Method / site Op-point Δ \\Delta w2t Δ \\Delta CLAP FAD Injection op (DiT residual) sour additive α = 0.1 \\alpha{=}0.1 + 0.419 +0.419 + 1.77 +1.77 561 \n561 additive α = 0.15 \\alpha{=}0.15 + 0.522", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false, "persistedOutputPath": "/inspire/qb-ilm/project/video-generation/chenxie-25019/hyr/iHateTheWorld555.github.io/.claude-review/projects/-inspire-qb-ilm-project-video-generation-chenxie-25019-hyr-iHateTheWorld555-github-io/5f6b4c4f-7999-4c36-8879-0ad9909619fb/tool-results/b4nxopiz1.txt", "persistedOutputSize": 63876}}
